{"tid":1304760,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢夢到七一嗰日達哥企得好前","createTime":"2019-07-10T16:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T19:41:08.000Z","uid":269148,"like":9,"dislike":101,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3ed4b65cb05eb913223fee282a9df2daecbfeb","tid":1304760,"uid":269148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"發夢夢到佢嗰日一個人單槍匹馬<br />\n揸著支螺絲起子<br />\n&ldquo;一野轟落去&rdquo;<br />\n塊玻璃炸到稀巴爛<br />\n大力得滯鐵閘都爆埋<br />\n一睄到裡面有警察<br />\n即刻當機立斷丟個自製煙霧<br />\n不忙叫一聲&ldquo;吔啦契弟&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;死仔包&rdquo;<br />\n結果啲差佬走曬<br />\n暴徒全面進場<br />\n達哥頭也不回飄然而去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後喺龍和道畀人拉咗<br />\n一路上警車一路叫&ldquo;屌解呀&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;公平咩&rdquo; &ldquo;公平咩&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n希望達哥最後無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地對你唔住林義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf697353e84a0946e4af372cfb5b66d985f6f0ec","tid":1304760,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e0c078f4e1650038118471f015ffca2c819fb4","tid":1304760,"uid":30604,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:49:14.000Z","msg":"On9當有趣"},{"pid":"d300f86cb92238c42b16f6d59f79f8074ed046c8","tid":1304760,"uid":269148,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:49:22.000Z","msg":"達哥份人好低調<br />\n本來叫我唔好講出嚟"},{"pid":"5169bdf1940155ea18014f589590a3398cdad15f","tid":1304760,"uid":216780,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:49:28.000Z","msg":"柒少陣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f841f0